### Spring Boot Student CRUD API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/students

### 1. Get all students
GET {{baseUrl}}

### 2. Get student by ID (existing student)
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### 3. Get student by ID (non-existing student)
GET {{baseUrl}}/999

### 4. Create a new student
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Johnson",
  "age": 21
}

### 5. Create another student
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Williams",
  "age": 23
}

### 6. Update an existing student
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "age": 25
}

### 7. Update a non-existing student
PUT {{baseUrl}}/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Non Existing",
  "age": 30
}

### 8. Delete a student
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/2

### 9. Delete a non-existing student
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/999

### 10. Get all students after modifications
GET {{baseUrl}}
